enough manpower.

00:01:42.730 --> 00:01:44.980
There's not enough eye
doctors in the world

00:01:44.980 --> 00:01:46.780
to be able to take
care of everyone.

00:01:46.780 --> 00:01:48.850
So this is really
the only chance

00:01:48.850 --> 00:01:53.020
to be able to get the people
who need care into treatment.

00:01:53.020 --> 00:01:56.290
To be able to identify them
and make sure that they're

00:01:56.290 --> 00:01:58.170
able to get treated.

00:01:58.170 --> 00:01:59.086
TIMOTHY JORDAN: I see.

